file.name: enumerations.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Whatever
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /foo/{intEnum}:
    post:
      operationId: doFoo
      x-jvm-package: foo
      parameters:
      - in: path
        name: intEnum
        required: true
        schema:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/IntEnum'
      - in: query
        name: longEnum
        schema:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/LongEnum'
      - in: query
        name: stringEnum
        schema:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/StringEnum'
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/IntEnum'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/IntEnum'
        '201':
          description: "Created"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/StringEnum'
        '202':
          description: "Accepted"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LongEnum'
components:
  schemas:
    StringEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - v1
        - v2
        - i like spaces
    IntEnum:
      type: integer
      format: int32
      enum:
        - 1
        - 2
        - 3
    LongEnum:
      type: integer
      format: int64
      enum:
        - 1
        - 2
        - 3
